<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Redis - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/redis/</link><description>Redis - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/redis/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Redisson编解码器创建异常</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/redisson%E7%BC%96%E8%A7%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/redisson%E7%BC%96%E8%A7%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="redisson编解码器创建异常">Redisson编解码器创建异常</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Redisson默认使用Kryo编解码器时，若类加载器环境复杂（如OSGi、热部署）或类无默认构造函数，会导致编解码器初始化失败，显式指定FstCodec或JsonJacksonCodec并确保类可被正确加载可规避此问题。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="问题现象">问题现象</h2>
<p>线上服务启动时偶发报错：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">org.redisson.client.RedisException: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Codec for class xxx not found
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    at org.redisson.codec.Kryo5Codec$1.encode(Kryo5Codec.java:xx)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Caused by: com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoException: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Unable to find class: com.example.UserDTO</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="影响范围">影响范围</h3>
<ul>
<li>服务启动阶段约30%概率失败</li>
<li>影响缓存读写功能，但Redis服务本身正常</li>
<li>重启可能恢复，但不可接受</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="排查过程">排查过程</h2>
<h3 id="第一步确认编解码器配置">第一步：确认编解码器配置</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 原有配置（未显式指定，使用默认值）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Config</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">config</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Config</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">useClusterServers</span><span class="p">().</span><span class="na">addNodeAddress</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;redis://...&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">未设置</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">codec</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="n">默认使用</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Kryo5Codec</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第二步分析类加载环境">第二步：分析类加载环境</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">项目使用</span> <span class="n">Spring</span> <span class="n">Boot</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="err">热部署</span> <span class="n">devtools</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">├──</span> <span class="err">主类加载器：</span><span class="n">AppClassLoader</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">├──</span> <span class="n">devtools</span> <span class="err">重启类加载器：</span><span class="n">RestartClassLoader</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">└──</span> <span class="n">Kryo</span> <span class="err">内部缓存的</span> <span class="n">Class</span> <span class="err">引用来自旧类加载器</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">问题：热部署后类加载器变化，</span><span class="n">Kryo缓存的Class引用失效</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第三步复现验证">第三步：复现验证</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 本地复现步骤</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">1</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">启动应用</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="n">写入缓存</span><span class="err">（</span><span class="n">Kryo注册类</span><span class="err">）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">2</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">修改代码触发</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">devtools</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">热重启</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">3</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">再次读写缓存</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">→</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">抛出</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">KryoException</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="根因分析">根因分析</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>因素</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Kryo默认行为</td>
          <td>缓存Class引用以提升序列化性能</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>热部署机制</td>
          <td>devtools使用RestartClassLoader重新加载类</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>引用失效</td>
          <td>Kryo缓存的Class来自旧类加载器，热部署后无法匹配新类加载器的类</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>默认无参构造</td>
          <td>部分DTO类缺少默认构造函数，Kryo无法实例化</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="解决方案">解决方案</h2>
<h3 id="方案一更换编解码器推荐">方案一：更换编解码器（推荐）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 显式使用 JsonJacksonCodec，避免类加载器依赖</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Config</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">config</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Config</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setCodec</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">JsonJacksonCodec</span><span class="p">());</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// JSON序列化，不缓存Class引用</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">useClusterServers</span><span class="p">().</span><span class="na">addNodeAddress</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;redis://...&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>编解码器</th>
          <th>优点</th>
          <th>缺点</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Kryo5Codec</td>
          <td>序列化体积小、速度快</td>
          <td>类加载器敏感、需无参构造</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>FstCodec</td>
          <td>性能接近Kryo</td>
          <td>同样存在类加载器问题</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>JsonJacksonCodec</td>
          <td>兼容性好、可读性强</td>
          <td>体积大、速度慢</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>TypedJsonJacksonCodec</td>
          <td>带类型信息</td>
          <td>兼容性和体积的平衡</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="方案二禁用热部署开发环境">方案二：禁用热部署（开发环境）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c"># application.yml</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">spring</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">devtools</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">restart</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">enabled</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c"># 开发环境若无需热部署可关闭</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="方案三确保类可被正确加载">方案三：确保类可被正确加载</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 为DTO添加无参构造函数</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">UserDTO</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">implements</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Serializable</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">final</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">serialVersionUID</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">1L</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="c1">// 必须：无参构造</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">UserDTO</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="c1">// 业务构造</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">UserDTO</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">id</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">name</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="复盘与预防">复盘与预防</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>措施</th>
          <th>执行方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>编码规范</td>
          <td>所有缓存对象必须实现Serializable、保留无参构造</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>配置检查</td>
          <td>Redisson配置必须显式指定Codec，禁止依赖默认值</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>环境统一</td>
          <td>开发和生产使用相同的Codec配置</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>升级评估</td>
          <td>升级Redisson版本时评估Codec兼容性变化</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
