<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1主从复制延迟导致数据不一致">问题1：主从复制延迟导致数据不一致</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：网络延迟、从节点处理慢
<strong>解决</strong>：监控复制偏移量、强制读主库（关键读）、延迟阈值告警</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Redis发布订阅</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97/redis%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97/redis%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="redis发布订阅">Redis发布订阅</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Redis Pub/Sub通过频道实现简单的消息广播，适合实时性要求高的轻量级通知场景，但不支持持久化、确认和消费组，无法替代专业的消息队列。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="redis-pubsub实现简单的消息广播轻量高效但缺乏可靠性和扩展性">Redis Pub/Sub实现简单的消息广播，轻量高效但缺乏可靠性和扩展性</h2>
<h3 id="基本模型频道channel和模式pattern">基本模型：频道（Channel）和模式（Pattern）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">发布者                    Redis服务器                    订阅者
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |                         |                            |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |  PUBLISH news &#34;hello&#34;   |                            |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   | ----------------------&gt; |                            |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |                         | ---- PUSH &#34;hello&#34; --------&gt; | Subscriber-1 (SUBSCRIBE news)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |                         | ---- PUSH &#34;hello&#34; --------&gt; | Subscriber-2 (SUBSCRIBE news)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |                         |                            |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">模式订阅：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  Subscriber-3: PSUBSCRIBE news.*
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  可接收 news.sport, news.tech 等频道消息</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>命令</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Redis核心数据结构</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/redis%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/redis%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="redis核心数据结构">Redis核心数据结构</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Redis通过底层六种数据结构（SDS、双向链表、压缩列表、哈希表、跳表、整数数组）实现对外五种数据类型，每种类型针对特定场景优化，理解底层实现是选择正确数据结构和预估内存的关键。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="redis对外提供五种数据类型底层通过六种内部数据结构实现每种类型针对特定场景优化">Redis对外提供五种数据类型，底层通过六种内部数据结构实现，每种类型针对特定场景优化</h2>
<h3 id="string最基础的二进制安全字符串">String：最基础的二进制安全字符串</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">底层实现：SDS（Simple Dynamic String）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">struct sdshdr {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    int len;      // 已使用长度
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    int free;     // 未使用长度
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    char buf[];   // 字符数组
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">特点：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 二进制安全（可存储图片、序列化对象）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- O(1)获取长度
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 预分配空间，减少扩容
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 最大512MB</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>String的典型应用</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>命令</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>缓存对象</td>
          <td>SET / GET</td>
          <td>存储JSON/Protobuf序列化数据</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>计数器</td>
          <td>INCR / DECR</td>
          <td>原子加减，适合限流统计</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分布式锁</td>
          <td>SETNX + EXPIRE</td>
          <td>原子获取锁</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>会话存储</td>
          <td>SETEX</td>
          <td>带过期时间的缓存</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>共享配置</td>
          <td>GET / SET</td>
          <td>全局配置中心</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 计数器应用</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">INCR page:view:1001        <span class="c1"># 文章1001的浏览量+1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">INCRBY page:view:1001 <span class="m">10</span>   <span class="c1"># 批量增加</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET page:view:1001
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 分布式锁</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">SET lock:order:123 NX EX <span class="m">30</span>  <span class="c1"># 原子设置锁，30秒过期</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="hash适合存储对象的键值对集合">Hash：适合存储对象的键值对集合</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
